                           <locus target="#75va">f. 75va</locus>
                           <desc>-vb: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#75va">75va</locus>: ለዝ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ገድለ፡ አቡነ፡ ዘርእ፡[sic] ቡሩክ፡
