                              ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት። {ዘወሃቦ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ነህብ።} ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡
                              ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዞ፡ ለይኩን፡ ከመ፡ አርዮስ። {ተፈጸመ፡ በ፲፱፻፳፩፡ ዓመተ።}</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note mentions the name of the donor Gabra Tǝnśāʾe and the
                              church dedicated to Zarʾa Buruk, under the authority of Mikāʾel Nǝhbi.
                              The name of the latter, and the date of the completion of the writing,
                              1921 A.M. (= 1928/29 A.D.) seem to have been added later, but possibly
                              in the same hand. </note>
                        </item>
